Heidi Klum, 49, looked incredible as she stripped down to a skimpy black, string bikini, for her latest Instagram post.The mum-of-four donned a bandeau bikini and slipped into a mini skirt for the sultry clip.She filmed herself dancing to Light My Fire by Gwen Stefani and wore large sunglasses before unveiling her makeup-free face.The model’s blonde locks swept over her shoulders as she showed off her moves.Sharing the clip to her 9.7 million followers, Heidi captioned the post: “#KeepDancing.”